              &mt LGUI A  &mt LALT R  &mt LSHFT S  &mt LCTRL T  &kp G                   &kp M    &mt RCTRL N  &mt RSHFT E  &mt RALT I  &mt RGUI O
&lt 3 ESCAPE  &kp Z       &kp X       &kp C        &kp D        &kp V                   &kp K    &kp H        &kp COMMA    &kp DOT     &kp FSLH    &kp BSLH
                                      &kp DEL      &lt 1 TAB    &mt LEFT_SHIFT SPACE    &kp RET  &lt 2 ESC    &kp BSPC
